{
  "id": "adv_bond_rio_01_01",
  "title": "神崎莉央1",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――LizNoirデビューの少し前",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A little before LizNoir debut",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "（ふわぁ～……ここのところ、学校の授業で）\n（居眠りしがちね……良くないわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Hu-wa~… Recently‚ I’ve been falling asleep）\n（a lot during class at school… that's not good）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 2.3666667143,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio002.m4a",
      "text": "（デビューが決まって、毎日レッスン漬けだからって）\n（気が緩んでいたわね。しっかりしないと）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（After debut was decided and continued to take lessons every day‚）\n（getting a little too relaxed. I have to do better）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.3666671593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 11.4000033351
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.1333304053
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio003.m4a",
      "text": "（それにしても、あの子……）\n（葵と私、うまくやっていけるのかしら？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（By the way‚ that girl…）\n（Aoi and I‚ can we get along?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.133333826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio004.m4a",
      "text": "ダンスは確かに凄いけど\nそれ以外がマイペース過ぎなのよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Dance is definitely great‚\nbut everything else is just her own tempo",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.333333826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 26.3333366667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio005.m4a",
      "text": "私だけならともかく、三枝さんにまでタメ口だし\n……でも、あの子年下なのよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Even if it's just me‚ but she speaks informally to Saegusa-san‚ too\n…But‚ that girl is younger than me",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.3666671593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 39.7000004927
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio006.m4a",
      "text": "私がしっかり指導しなきゃダメね\nデビュー後もあんな態度じゃ、葵がマスコミに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I have to guide her tightly\nIf she continues to behave like that even after her debut‚ Aoi will be in mass media…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 39.7000004927,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6033.3333333
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 45.733337652
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-aoi001.m4a",
      "text": "僕がどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's wrong with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 46.233333826,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio007.m4a",
      "text": "だから、貴方にはもう少し礼儀やマナーを\n――って、葵！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ you should be more polite and mannered\n――Wait‚ Aoi!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9666671593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-aoi002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央の制服姿は初めて見たよ\n似合ってるね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's my first time seeing Rio's school uniform\nLooks good",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 53.3333350975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 53.3333379382
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 57.8333333174
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そう？　ありがとう\n――って、そうじゃなくて！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "R-Really? Thank you\n--No‚ that's not it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.8333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 63.23333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio009.m4a",
      "text": "こんな所で何してるのよ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you doing in a place like this?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.2333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-aoi003.m4a",
      "text": "今日は学校が早く終わったから莉央を迎えに来たんだ\n最近、疲れてるみたいだから気になって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "School finished early today so I came to pick up Rio\nLately‚ I've been concerned about how tired you look",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.5333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 73.03333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio010.m4a",
      "text": "つ、疲れてなんかないわよ。私のことはいいの\n貴方よりずっと年上なんだから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "N-No‚ I'm no tired. I'm fine\nI'm much older than you!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-aoi004.m4a",
      "text": "その割には、さっき大きなあくびをしてたけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Despite that‚ you yawned loudly just now",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.899999984,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 79.9
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 84.2666666507
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio011.m4a",
      "text": "さっきの、見られていたのね……失態だわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You saw‚ what I did just now…… It was a mistake",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.2666666507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 89.1333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "aoi",
      "speakerName": "井川葵",
      "speakerNameEn": "Aoi",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-aoi.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-aoi005.m4a",
      "text": "それより早くレッスンに行こうよ\n疲れてるなら僕、おんぶしようか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's go to lesson sooner than that\nIf you're tired‚ should I carry you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.1333333174,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01/sud_vo_adv_bond_rio_01_01-rio012.m4a",
      "text": "いらないわよ！　もう、生意気言わないの！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No neeed! Seriously‚ don't get cocky!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 94.7666666507,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyotown-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyotown-00-noon",
      "startTime": 94.76667
    }
  ]
